arStrings.szText: “What is this camp you spoke of?”
Edgar has been hiding people from the Knights inside some abandoned buildings south of Caldeum.
We thought they would be safe there, but no one is safe from Osric and his Inquisitors. He’ll never stop hunting them.
Will you go and help Edgar? He wasn’t always good, but what he’s doing now is. He deserves a chance to atone for his sins.
Suna sees the player as maybe the only force that could keep Edgar from getting killed by Osric.
